> Your Complete UPSC Civil Services Examination Preparation Platform

## ✨ Features

- 📚 **12 Complete Subjects** with micro-syllabus, books, videos, PYQs
- 🔗 **500+ Curated Resources** — websites, YouTube, PDFs, apps
- 🏆 **Topper Strategies** from AIR 1-10 rankers
- 📰 **Daily Current Affairs** with smart tagging
- 🧠 **Interactive Quiz** with timer, analytics, progress tracking
- 📅 **Study Planner** with drag-drop and templates
- 📖 **120+ Term Glossary** with search and bookmarks
- 🧮 **Score Calculator** for Prelims, Mains, Interview
- 🔍 **Global Search** across all content (Cmd+K)
- 🌓 **Dark Mode** support
- 📱 **Fully Responsive** design

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- Next.js 15 + React 19 + TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS + Shadcn/ui
- Framer Motion animations
- Recharts for data visualization

